snippet: In a Feb. 18 story about a new commission on cybersecurity, The Associated Press erroneously reported that a breach of sensitive personal information of U.S. federal employees and others in 2015 included classified documents. It did not....
lead_paragraph: In a Feb. 18 story about a new commission on cybersecurity, The Associated Press erroneously reported that a breach of sensitive personal information of U.S. federal employees and others in 2015 included classified documents. It did not.
